{"tid":2060045,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥美娟倡開放健康碼予到內地工作港人使用","createTime":"2020-06-11T10:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T10:58:57.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c78eac198d424f1b80c45f9dabadeb4fb9528044","tid":2060045,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"工聯會立法會議員麥美娟表示，得悉政府準備推出的健康碼計劃，暫時只有不足10間檢測中心與政府合作，期望政府尋找更多檢測中心，以及容許更多市民參與計劃。<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟建議政府應與更多檢測機構合作，否則擔心檢測中心的承載力及檢測價格高昂，亦不應過分局限使用健康碼的人數，並開放予到內地工作的港人。<br />\n<br />\n她又建議政府應為特定群組，例如學生或基層工人津貼檢測費用，同時考慮逐步開放關口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531507-20200611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531507-20200611.htm&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=8b9c663c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531507-20200611.htm&h=ca638a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531507-20200611.htm</a>"},{"pid":"47eab1eb52ef0f360f8a15d5fb656989d8b11abf","tid":2060045,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"要死上去開工既一早走晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}